{"tid":833214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實身邊好多你睇唔岀要取暖嘅人","createTime":"2018-09-23T10:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T12:48:07.000Z","uid":132401,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"451e80a1df72fcda73266d92e5cbc3160097ac08","tid":833214,"uid":132401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"係一個普通嘅學生<br />\n就快grad 但係仲好迷失 唔知自己想點<br />\n人地睇落好多好多朋友 仲要比人話大袋<br />\n聽完我成日都笑笑口就算 因為無人會明白內心孤獨<br />\n單身半年 其實呢個年紀仲讀緊書點會無人追<br />\n係有啊 但就係好似每個都差啲差啲<br />\n講唔到差咩 定係本身想要嘅始終得唔到 有個無可能嘅人係心<br />\n嗰種挫敗感真係就算你比人點吹捧都cover唔到<br />\n連玩都玩到心好攰 識幾多人都填唔飽嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n今日又大一歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都估唔到自己會開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07de3ca73648b6bf1dc3f540f83edddfc0da962b","tid":833214,"uid":5399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"單身得嗰半年就睇開少少啦<br />\n不過我都喺到諗 個個都入哂穩定關係<br />\n唔通拍唔到拖係自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nanyway 生日快樂 學下自己面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b39ba7f8027557478739f88373de3c4336fba1","tid":833214,"uid":190818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc14d4698770fe9edacde99d3daa3249294c0c65","tid":833214,"uid":71441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"十五志於學，三十而立。<br />\n專心挑戰自己，增廣見聞，令自己成為一個博學多材嘅真漢子喇。感情大可以順其自然，有麝自然香。<br />\n生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9519f2bd289de051f3e6a9d31a984b8cc7ca46fb","tid":833214,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"無人想知你想唔想取暖"},{"pid":"f9597c8b172d02f4d6e76963c6541012b7ae3d36","tid":833214,"uid":122647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n我向朋友同事面前佢地都覺得我eq高唔會冧添<br />\n但我晚晚失眠又有邊知知"},{"pid":"7fc0f62407d71d1b856cfc140da01b664f2636df","tid":833214,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"同意"}]}